* 2017-02-06 -- 0.1.2
 * Added mount.gridfs script which behaves similar to other mount progs
 * Fixed bug during initial mount when creating new gridfs collection
 * Allow database and collection to be specified in --mongodb-uri argument
 * Changed setup.py to read from supporting files (LICENSE, README.md, etc.)

* 2016-01-13 -- 0.1.1
 * 'stat' failed on other nodes while a file is created/written.
 * Better error handling if a file is read while it's still written.

* 2015-05-07 -- 0.1.0
 * Initial version
